author: chengchen1993
body:
There are three pixel clients that are no more used by 2017:
1) pixeltracking_timing_dqm_sourceclient-live_cfg.py (first implementation of a client with Tracking for Pixel Phase 1)
2) pixel_timingScan_dqm_sourceclient-live_cfg.py (as the above, but more recent)
3) pixel_up_dqm_sourceclient-live_cfg.py (specific client for the Phase 1 pilot blade, used only few days in 2016)
title: Clean the online clients which are unused
